.TH halt 1 "2021-08-15"

.SH NAME
halt - Halt the machine

.SH SYNOPSIS
.SY halt
.YS

.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.I halt
utility causes the machine to shutdown.
It does that by killing the init process.

